  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dba \u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bud support to Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna President Professor GL Peiris said that since a candidate has been nominated from the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, support should be given to the candidate of the party and not to an outside candidate.",
        "He also mentioned that since Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna is the party with the largest number of members in the Parliament, it is possible for the candidate from Pudujana Peramuna to win.",
        "Professor Peiris said that Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma has already announced that he will stand for the election of the President which will be held on the 20th and that he is a very suitable candidate.",
        "He also said that Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna as a party has not taken a decision to support any other candidate"
      ],
